mock_interviews.title: Software Engineer - Full Stack Developer
mock_interviews.description: Comprehensive mock interview for full-stack development positions covering frontend, backend, and system design concepts.
mock_interviews.instructions: This interview will test your knowledge of web development, databases, APIs, and problem-solving skills. Be prepared for both technical and behavioral questions.

mock_interviews.title: Data Scientist - Machine Learning Engineer
mock_interviews.description: Mock interview focused on data science, machine learning algorithms, and statistical analysis for ML engineering roles.
mock_interviews.instructions: Expect questions on machine learning algorithms, data preprocessing, model evaluation, and Python programming. Some coding challenges will involve data manipulation.

mock_interviews.title: Frontend Developer - React Specialist
mock_interviews.description: Specialized mock interview for React developers focusing on component architecture, state management, and modern frontend practices.
mock_interviews.instructions: This interview covers React fundamentals, hooks, state management, performance optimization, and frontend best practices. Coding challenges will involve React components.

mock_interviews.title: Backend Developer - Python/Django
mock_interviews.description: Backend-focused mock interview covering server-side development, APIs, databases, and Python frameworks.
mock_interviews.instructions: Interview will cover Python programming, Django framework, database design, API development, and system architecture. Expect both theoretical and practical questions.

mock_interviews.title: DevOps Engineer - Cloud Infrastructure
mock_interviews.description: DevOps and cloud infrastructure interview covering CI/CD, containerization, monitoring, and cloud platforms.
mock_interviews.instructions: This interview focuses on DevOps practices, cloud services, infrastructure as code, monitoring, and automation. Practical scenarios will be discussed.

mock_interviews.title: Mobile Developer - React Native
mock_interviews.description: Mobile development interview focusing on React Native, mobile app architecture, and cross-platform development.
mock_interviews.instructions: Interview covers React Native development, mobile UI/UX principles, app store deployment, and mobile-specific challenges. Coding will involve mobile components.

mock_interviews.title: System Design - Senior Engineer
mock_interviews.description: Senior-level system design interview covering scalability, architecture patterns, and distributed systems.
mock_interviews.instructions: This interview focuses on system design principles, scalability challenges, microservices architecture, and distributed systems. Expect whiteboard-style design questions.

mock_interviews.title: QA Engineer - Test Automation
mock_interviews.description: Quality assurance interview covering test automation, testing frameworks, and quality processes.
mock_interviews.instructions: Interview covers testing methodologies, automation frameworks, bug tracking, and quality assurance processes. Some coding challenges will involve test scripts.
